{"tid":876274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金巴司機疑「揸錯車」乘客搭去澳門變珠海：個人呆咗","createTime":"2018-10-25T13:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T09:17:59.000Z","uid":82917,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8b86e496820828f06af74311c05d9874b6297287","tid":876274,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/213733_0cc022f757ccd03dc63954c98d63d231.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F213733_0cc022f757ccd03dc63954c98d63d231.png&h=05b58e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《蘋果》接獲市民黎小姐投訴指，懷疑因司機沒有港澳車牌、只得中港車牌但「揸錯車」，將全車乘客接載至珠海口岸。(讀者提供圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/213750_b77be6fc0d95b97ec6033c03fe102c76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F213750_b77be6fc0d95b97ec6033c03fe102c76.png&h=36c01906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎小姐指最終在2時多到達澳門口岸，較原定時間遲了約1小時。(讀者提供圖片)<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋昨日（24日）通車，來往各口岸的「金巴」穿梭巴士「港珠線」及「港澳線」亦開始營運，《蘋果》接獲市民黎小姐投訴，指今午乘坐12時半出發「港澳線」巴士，車程原定約40分鐘，但疑因司機沒有港澳車牌、只得中港車牌但「揸錯車」，將全車乘客接載至珠海口岸，到埗後更一度要求乘客下車，自行由珠海到澳門，經協調才交另一司機、開另一輛「金巴」接載乘客到澳門。<br />\n<br />\n黎小姐今午第一次乘坐日間票價65元的「金巴」，打算到澳門探望朋友，但就遇上司機疑似「上錯車」。她表示，巴士駛至旅程中後段時，已有乘客陸續發現駛向了珠海方向，有人向司機查詢，但未獲正面回覆，最終巴士在珠海口岸停泊，司機表示無法接載乘客到澳門，一度要求乘客自行由珠海轉車到澳門，黎小姐直言當時「好無奈，成個人呆咗。」<br />\n<br />\n乘客對此不滿鼓譟，該名司機下車跟珠海口岸職員商討後，才安排了另一輛「金巴」及另一名司機，將受影響乘客由珠海口岸送至澳門，最終全車乘客在2時多才到達澳門口岸，較原定時間遲了約1小時。黎小姐指出，一眾乘客按指示登車，懷疑是有關司機「揸錯車」，「我哋喺現場聽到司機同職員對話，估計係司機只得中港車牌，無港澳車牌，所以根本揸唔到去澳門。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》已向「金巴」營辨商「港珠澳大橋穿梭巴士」查詢事件，正等候回覆。"},{"pid":"872385587715856b37c627dee6ccce915c6bf76b","tid":876274,"uid":82917,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔撚係掛</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/214121_5b2ffe0215b7a1d52911b12233fe9a40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F214121_5b2ffe0215b7a1d52911b12233fe9a40.png&h=f61e0d61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b327c3de2d39d467690c6a70a6d8fdf67cc6a7d0","tid":876274,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陰公"},{"pid":"2ddc1a419a1e393862649c3258f91d740632a90e","tid":876274,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"美今日咁早醒?我岩先收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac3c8b783ba52b755e39b4c120a0d3bbb2b89aa","tid":876274,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ddc1a419a1e393862649c3258f91d740632a90e","tid":876274,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"美今日咁早醒?我岩先收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:59:52.000Z","msg":"考試呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88d6191ec679460dd3b36cd27091a8af7ee3211","tid":876274,"uid":75610,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"賣豬仔咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554001bc4bf9818ab174d53395c9e078800764df","tid":876274,"uid":183383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ac3c8b783ba52b755e39b4c120a0d3bbb2b89aa","tid":876274,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ddc1a419a1e393862649c3258f91d740632a90e","tid":876274,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"美今日咁早醒?我岩先收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"re